title: Voyage to the Bottom of the Sea S04E23 Attack! AVI
description:
VOYAGE TO THE BOTTOM OF THE SEA
SPECIAL EDITION
SEASON 4 EPISODES


By popular demand, TooleMan TV presents the final 13 episodes of
Voyage to the Bottom of the Sea
in high-quality compact size
AVI format X264 video with Dolby Digital audio

Each episode has been remastered from excellent broadcast recordings for the best video and audio.



Episode 23, first aired March 10, 1968

"ATTACK!"

A renegade (Skip Homeier) works against his alien leader (Kevin Hagen) to help the men of the Seaview thwart a full-scale assault by alien flying saucers.

Nelson: Richard Basehart. Crane: David Hedison. Komal: Kevin Hagen. Kowalski: Del Monroe. Chief: Terry Becker. Morton: Bob Dowdell.
